Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿银
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声响太大 吵醒您了吗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐描绘的蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这个肮脏的国度 高举仁义之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后唤来国内的有志之士 征服那充满恶棍的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那群俄罗斯人有多棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过这段时间的战斗已经不用多说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将在那群人中杀出条血路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后对巴拉莱卡挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙必定是个适合与这白鞘交手的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我与阿银一直走到了今天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 今后也要在这一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往罗阿那普拉…也一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福工作看来能顺利结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的事莫斯科来的后任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.57,0:01:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会接下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾 不能看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 石黑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚进去的三人组…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊什么啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的白人二名 日本人一名 你确认身份了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了ICPO的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可还没找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求国际刑警派来援手的事怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说派了个叫河野的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正往这边过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个白种女人 肯定与鹫峰香砂之争有关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好足立区的保龄球馆枪战也是她的手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 总之绝对要盯好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有话要说的应该是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴拉莱卡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克 你是想说上次那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经饶了你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你还有更大的奢望？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你想让我说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若只是要我听的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言 请再听我一言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情能就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请你将鹫峰组彻底击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到让那组织不可能继续存在下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到杂草不留 彻底的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样 才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原 来 如 此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在现在情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能使公主返回日常世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是恶棍啊 洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正确的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的恶棍生涯前途无量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please,forgive my delay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you must be exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,from these long discussions
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了冗长的会谈 想必累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我们这边也算了结件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前嫌 让它就这么冰释 今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr.Kousa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We must prepare plans over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,who will succeed us in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然今后的任务我们将交由后任接手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If certain contingencies should occur in our absence
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若我们不在期间有什么问题发生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,it will be difficult for us to respond properly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是很难做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish to know your state of readiness over firearms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你们的情况 知道你们的武装情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it adequate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是否万全？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是什么能自豪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和其他组织比起来 就算只论枪支数量也是天壤之别
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还从夏威夷那里的家伙买过机关枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Would you oblige me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the bullets as well
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看一下子弹的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quite competent bodyguard you have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you have any back up means of protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 您有位优秀的保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否带了备用的第二把呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都谈到这地步了 翻脸对他们也没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很难收场 交给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Absolutely atrocious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Keep up with me,you brat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把枪真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Take a look,sergeant
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Atrocious,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I doubt if even lowlife punks in the gutter would use guns like this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连乡下的小混混都不会拿这种枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Absolutely atrocious
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骇人听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a hideous it is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不成体统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you ever stopped to consider
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有试想过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What it would feel like to be shot with a gun like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被这样的枪 击中之人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法与无耻地拿着这种枪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安泽先生 是枪声
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯进宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要强制执行了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这枪还不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军曹 时间如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题 大尉阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这要如何向大头目解释？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大头目曾叫我“开战 把这化为一片火海”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忠实地执行了它罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克 这是“你的枪”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿去作个纪念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不准备拿自己拿不起的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扣过这扳机的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军曹 那把枪也丢在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们返回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宅内之人 全都不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是本厅四课的安泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是本厅警备部一课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责本次事件的石黑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于刚才的枪声 想请您说明一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦同我们走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克 替我传句话给鹫峰组的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科旅馆将从现在 单方面停止交战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你希望根绝的鹫峰组
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经四分五裂潜入地下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比你想的更有战略眼光哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从布鲁伽基毕利得到的俘虏情报来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说组员如此相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后那位公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将带着他们 到罗阿那普拉高举起一面旗帜来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不去那不去 偏偏是那罗阿那普拉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎接的人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我让出路来 你们这些民警
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 话还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使已在狸穴等您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉提蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 安泽先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是“外”开头的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.68,Note,NTP,0,0,0,,“外”开头：指有法外治权
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕 逮捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找的是我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别为杂鱼分神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见 民警们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若找我有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯大使馆的一等书记官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,V.N.瓦里基纳夫 会随时恭候各位大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 还是没赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际搜查官 河野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么听到枪声 却没逮捕她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场在宅邸内 只能随她们说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们到底是谁 查出是谁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是条大鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘据在莫斯科
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在车臣和纽约都说得上话的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑手党组织“莫斯科旅馆”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的通称是“巴拉莱卡”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是莫斯科旅馆的大干部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我转台 现场呼叫中心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系正在市内巡逻的各PC
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有拍摄相貌吗 捕捉到她的脸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么至少要算上那个摩托牌照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只查出那个日本人的身份也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱薇 必须转达她战争的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不了三十分钟这一带连细菌都别想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢绝会面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 你就在船上跟她联系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离出航时刻近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪 雪绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我们去玛丽阿扎斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:13.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连四眼中学生都开始干绑匪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连驾车都会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够不良的吧 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个去罗阿那普拉扎脚的闹剧是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如你所说 站在黄昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有些事看得清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫斯科旅馆已经宣布停战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴拉莱卡的话有什么保障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视所有条约为无物 背叛 对仁义以利牙相向的狂犬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫谁去信任她？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拦截啊 不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在罗阿那普拉重组组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果从内心去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是件令人期待的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那也不过是湖中倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我和阿银在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹫峰的代纹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹫峰的招牌就在此地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有落地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是要转回那儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从一开始就出生在黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与黑夜为伴长大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说“试试这种生活”的愚痴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也已经从中得到了不少乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究 这就是现实之道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在莫斯科旅馆面前 我没有当人质的价值哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那请你作个防弹衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然 作个见证人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见证这场乾坤一掷的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的只会是屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有在其中绽放的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了吗 冈岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 是黑社会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位 作战结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回罗阿那普拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不够了 决不能先踩刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克 我说过的 她已经是活死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说香砂会由内乱而灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先将组之重臣 少主板东次男背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并残忍屠杀之人还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨敌 莫斯科旅馆首魁巴拉莱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活于侠 贯彻仁 报答义 乃我等的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不存在什么必须受其制约的义理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是你的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让出路来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿银 已不在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐 真不该带您来“这儿”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些人 最终都殊途同归
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管走到哪儿 都不是什么好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是只有像我们这样的人才能来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不这么认为吗…那边的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾有过使你不用走上与巴拉莱卡一样道路的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以为你应该选择那个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是我想错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非为了什么黑社会的面子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你挣扎着想与黑夜同化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我站在黄昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才能把某些事看得清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该让阿银放下刀 与他一同逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后两人周游四方 在谁也不认识我们的地方摆摊开店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道不挺可笑的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的你到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我曾经很多次想过就这样生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我已经把筛子投了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想 集市要是能一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人唱戏卖艺 有人开店摆摊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边还有阿银在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是多么快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的慢到死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有泥土棺子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却打算“活”下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱薇 莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 眼前漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.81,0:18:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把那女人的一言引了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那儿 才是真正的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那句话 现在倒在血泊里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.84,0:18:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有点痛 忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脚抬起来 莱薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再给你包扎一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的内心被扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做着期望通过这样好起来的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你的头脑 却好到了无法用它欺骗自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十一人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从投出了筛子的那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于我的命令而被杀之人的数目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的城市 塞满了这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然梦已醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那片土地 已对我们太过遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我为这一切的骚动都予以完结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看那家伙 洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会受创伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天不见如隔三秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 那张加拿大籍中国人的假护照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派上用场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达奇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我在听着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人就像筛子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己将自己投向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道个说过这种话的法国人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·P·萨鲁托鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实主义派的哲学家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可震撼到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 要提早给往三个笼子里塞五只蛋进去的家伙开个风孔 这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 也对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一回来就会有新工作等着你办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后天之前要想办法把堆积如山的枪支送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 回见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飞的时刻到了哦 搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴拉莱卡小姐给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座罗阿那普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个能用枪的力量和酒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及暴力支配一切的美妙城市
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其实也没什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.13,0:22:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算站在这里的黄昏下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见证发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着我们的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果怎样？ 日本之行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有巴拉莱卡大姐头在 有我们在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪儿还不都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁问你这个 我说的是洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人出去了那么久…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 这次总算“做”了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我带到棺材里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不会轻易就死的啦